== Turn Order ==

Turn order is determined by Speed stat:
* Higher Speed acts first
* Ties broken by character index
* Status effects can modify effective Speed

Formula:
```
Effective Speed = Base Speed × (1 + Equipment Bonus) - Status Penalty
```

