== Defense ==

=== Defend Command ===

Using Defend:
* Halves all incoming damage
* Guarantees acting last that turn
* Cannot be used with other commands

=== Guard Stat Effect ===

Physical damage reduction:
```
Damage = Attack - (Guard × 1.5)
Minimum damage = 1
```

