== Experience and Leveling ==

=== Experience Formula ===

```
EXP Gained = Base EXP × (1 + Level Difference Bonus)
```

Level difference affects EXP:
* Fighting stronger enemies: Bonus EXP
* Fighting weaker enemies: Reduced EXP

