== Enemy Scaling ==

The 7th Saga is known for its rubber-banding enemy difficulty:

=== Scaling Formula ===

```
Enemy Level = Player Level + Region Modifier
Enemy Stats = Base Stats × (1 + (Enemy Level / 10))
```

This means enemies always stay challenging regardless of grinding.

