== Escape Mechanics ==

=== Escape Rate ===

```
Escape Chance = (Party Speed / Enemy Speed) × 50%
Minimum: 10%
Maximum: 90%
```

Failed escape wastes the turn.

== Partner System ==

=== Partner Benefits ===

Having a partner provides:
* Combined HP pool in battle
* Shared turn (both can act)
* Combined rune effects
* Stat bonuses

=== Partner Commands ===

In two-character battles:
* Each character has separate commands
* Can coordinate attacks
* Both must be defeated to lose

